text: Commission on Higher Education (CHED) is the governing body covering both public and private higher education institutions in the Philippines, including its degree-granting programs. The CHED was established in May 18, 1994 through Republic Act 7722 or the Higher Education Act of 1994. ==Related pages== *Professional Regulation Commission (Philippines) ==Other websites== *CHED Philippines official website Category:Education in the Philippines Category:Government agencies of the Philippines
title: Commission on Higher Education (Philippines)
